# TradeOS / Hermes — Agent Context

## Project

Unified **AI Trading Operating System** (Track A) + **Hermes Protocol** (Track B).

## Stack

TypeScript, Next.js 15, React 19, Tailwind, Supabase Postgres (RLS), modular monorepo.

## Structure

- `apps/web` — dashboard shell
- `packages/core` — Zod schemas, RBAC helpers, pure functions
- `supabase/migrations` — schema + RLS
- `specs/011-screenshot-replay/` — current phase spec/plan/tasks
- `.specify/memory/constitution.md` — governance (read before coding)

## Non-Negotiables

1. Deterministic risk outranks AI; no live execution; broker read-only
2. `tenant_id` + RLS on all tenant data; real cross-tenant tests
3. Structured AI outputs with confidence + limitations
4. Build only the requested phase

## MVP Order

Journal → Risk → Briefing → Coach → Hermes backend/RBAC/providers/operator dashboard

## Current Phase

**Phase 11 Screenshot + Replay** — secure upload, chart AI review, trade replay sessions

See `specs/011-screenshot-replay/plan.md` and `quickstart.md`.
